      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "Faithful Tile Upscale - Topaz / SeedV2 2x2 (4 tiles)\n\nPipeline: Tile Crop -> preview tiles -> Extract (x4) -> Scale By Placeholder (x4) -> Tile Collect -> preview upscaled -> Tile Stitch -> preview + Save + print size.\n\nReplace each Tile Scale By / Placeholder with Topaz, SeedV2, ESRGAN, or another faithful upscaler.\ntile_metadata flows linearly: TileCropAM -> TileCollectAM (passthrough) -> TileStitchAM.\nFor SeedVR2: change method to 'seedv2' \u2014 grid_preset 'method default' will switch to 2x3 (square-ish tiles)."
      ]
    },
